{"tid":1965972,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"子瑜「水手高校服」萌照網炸鍋！  ^_^","createTime":"2020-04-09T22:16:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-10T06:21:24.000Z","uid":44730,"like":17,"dislike":196,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"50cee7cb3757b82100a1b3dc8a8fa3e9720294f3","tid":1965972,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T22:16:52.000Z","msg":"不錯的網炸鍋 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/01/11/000240_16550d59580159b79c69c6c3bfe8ed7d.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F01%2F11%2F000240_16550d59580159b79c69c6c3bfe8ed7d.gif&h=d2a26468&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/style/page/2020/04/08/200408-13236-4-InaMO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fstyle%2Fpage%2F2020%2F04%2F08%2F200408-13236-4-InaMO.jpg&h=544552b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然因武漢肺炎疫情，一連取消韓日多場演唱會，但女孩們可是一點都沒閒著，先是宣布將有實境節目《TIME TO TWICE》，（8）日晚上，官方社群更是公開子瑜、多賢、彩瑛換上「水手高校服」的超萌美照，尤其是子瑜還綁了可愛雙辮子頭，完全就是高校生模樣，惹得網友狂嘆：好想回學校上課喔！"},{"pid":"8fab88529028535959ceefd3a7da2988e3b4cb07","tid":1965972,"uid":44730,"like":3,"dislike":42,"score":-39,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T22:17:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/style/page/2020/04/08/200408-13236-5-bn0qk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fstyle%2Fpage%2F2020%2F04%2F08%2F200408-13236-5-bn0qk.jpg&h=43067e2f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/01/11/000240_16550d59580159b79c69c6c3bfe8ed7d.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F01%2F11%2F000240_16550d59580159b79c69c6c3bfe8ed7d.gif&h=d2a26468&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f4061257448eb3c034c6561104e40c6bc871d754","tid":1965972,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T22:17:14.000Z","msg":"日前才宣布將開錄實境節目《TIME TO TWICE》，讓許多防疫悶在家的粉絲們終於有了一點值得期待的事，而貼心的女孩們除了忙著錄節目也沒閒著，子瑜、Mina、彩瑛就換上學生制服，並寫著：「來去吃學校午餐啦！」"},{"pid":"0dab1f0acafcbda8f64dbba5976a822fa144f858","tid":1965972,"uid":205928,"like":7,"dislike":19,"score":-12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T22:17:27.000Z","msg":"幾young幾qq"},{"pid":"ed81db5ff0270c9f5704501c729edb2eab0297ca","tid":1965972,"uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T22:17:28.000Z","msg":"彩瑛換上海軍領的水手服，搭配一頭俐落短髮，直被網友笑稱：滿18了沒？而多賢和子瑜穿著一樣的白色翻領襯衫、搭配深藍色洋裝制服，只是Mina頭戴小圓帽，子瑜則綁上辮子展現活力，超萌的模樣讓網友直呼太可愛了！"},{"pid":"ba6bdaa010d0f1e971cd08a080ddc13b193e8daf","tid":1965972,"uid":44730,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T22:17:42.000Z","msg":"尤其是因疫情而停課的韓國粉絲們，更是舉手大喊：「好想回學校上課」、「可以跟她們當同學嗎」、「有這種同學我一定不會翹課」、「學生制服無敵」、「求同班」！"},{"pid":"28182740a0d5deb3d1c07879e199ef4ed8dd781c","tid":1965972,"uid":44730,"like":4,"dislike":11,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T22:17:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/style/bphoto/normal/2020/04/09/20200409-88958-15.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fstyle%2Fbphoto%2Fnormal%2F2020%2F04%2F09%2F20200409-88958-15.jpg&h=3865a226&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/01/11/000240_16550d59580159b79c69c6c3bfe8ed7d.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F01%2F11%2F000240_16550d59580159b79c69c6c3bfe8ed7d.gif&h=d2a26468&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"017f571133a028b5b8170d83ca43d4edf463ee0f","tid":1965972,"uid":44730,"like":19,"dislike":5,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T22:18:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/style/page/2020/04/08/200408-13236-6-gzCSn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fstyle%2Fpage%2F2020%2F04%2F08%2F200408-13236-6-gzCSn.jpg&h=40720177&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n畢業後「靠髮」大進化<br />\n<br />\n其實才20歲的子瑜，去年2月才從高中畢業，距離高校生時期並不久，不過眼尖的粉絲卻發現她的美又更進化了！最明顯的就是以前學生時期是「乖乖牌」黑長直髮，她也曾分享過因為上學方便、且「學生就該有學生的樣子」。"},{"pid":"1e52305f7194c3c20a6ebc71f4f07ece27af1d9e","tid":1965972,"uid":44730,"like":21,"dislike":6,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T22:18:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/style/page/2020/04/08/200408-13236-10-UhrQG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fstyle%2Fpage%2F2020%2F04%2F08%2F200408-13236-10-UhrQG.jpg&h=8d3ef684&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/style/page/2020/04/08/200408-13236-8-eQ7HK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fstyle%2Fpage%2F2020%2F04%2F08%2F200408-13236-8-eQ7HK.jpg&h=a2ce5787&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/style/page/2020/04/08/200408-13236-9-nyNfQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fstyle%2Fpage%2F2020%2F04%2F08%2F200408-13236-9-nyNfQ.jpg&h=df18a6ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/style/page/2020/04/08/200408-13236-7-lMzI9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fstyle%2Fpage%2F2020%2F04%2F08%2F200408-13236-7-lMzI9.jpg&h=5f558152&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過畢業後就整個大解禁，不但多次換上新髮色，也剪了瀏海、甚至做成捲髮造型，多變的模樣也讓她看起來更活潑許多。這回難得重溫學生造型，卻又有不同以往正牌高校妹的模樣，也讓人忍不住大嘆，子瑜果然怎樣都美！"},{"pid":"5919858759569fed370f30d82ab539ecfa0a36f8","tid":1965972,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"0dab1f0acafcbda8f64dbba5976a822fa144f858","tid":1965972,"uid":205928,"like":7,"dislike":19,"score":-12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T22:17:27.000Z","msg":"幾young幾qq"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T22:20:40.000Z","msg":"瀏海加分？ <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/01/11/000240_16550d59580159b79c69c6c3bfe8ed7d.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnai